find their lost Bitcoin.

301
00:11:30,630 --> 00:11:31,750
it's just not gonna happen.

302
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:33,700
Not your keys, not your crypto.

303
00:11:33,700 --> 00:11:35,070
Most people will buy their crypto

304
00:11:35,070 --> 00:11:38,030
on an exchange like
Coinbase, and keep it there.

305
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,370
And that's the issue.

306
00:11:39,370 --> 00:11:41,520
It's been said that it's
much more profitable

307
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:44,890
