320
00:12:14,210 --> 00:12:15,500
but it does have benefits,

321
00:12:15,500 --> 00:12:18,030
such as being faster and making it easier

322
00:12:18,030 --> 00:12:20,010
to trade or spend crypto.

323
00:12:20,010 --> 00:12:21,890
The second is a cold wallet,

324
00:12:21,890 --> 00:12:25,310
which is how I currently store
the majority of my crypto.

325
00:12:25,310 --> 00:12:27,930
This is typically not
connected to the internet,

326
00:12:27,930 --> 00:12:31,220
so while it may be more
secure, it's less convenient.

327
00:12:36,846 --> 00:12:38,146
to the wrong wallet.

328
00:12:38,146 --> 00:12:39,946
Sending crypto between your wallets

329
00:12:39,946 --> 00:12:41,686
