other wallet, nice and safely.

338
00:13:01,676 --> 00:13:03,416
To avoid this ever happening again,

339
00:13:03,416 --> 00:13:06,376
I now always transfer a
small amount of crypto first,

340
00:13:06,376 --> 00:13:08,416
